Date: 2026-06-30

Request: CROSS-REQ-05 - Portfolio Integration Assessment & Promotion Board Refresh

Workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This assessment is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Purpose

This assessment consolidates the Cross-Nucleus Integration Cycle and refreshes the portfolio advancement decision after the opportunity registry, dependency registry, ownership alignment and governance/execution boundary review.

It does not implement integrations, APIs, product functionality, MCP services, providers, governance execution, treasury execution, trading execution, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, wallet signing, on-chain writes or production readiness.

