## Portfolio Integration Readiness Summary

The ecosystem is integrated enough for one additional bounded, non-executive advancement cycle.

The best next target is `AxodusAPP Integration Expansion`, scoped to read-only presentation contracts and consumer alignment. This target has strong portfolio integration value and can avoid the blocked execution paths that constrain Marketplace, Academy, Mining, ACS, Trading, Defi, Dex and Lottery.

